Verification of Ramanujan congruences:
  p(5k+4) ≡ 0 (mod KEY_SUM):
    p(  4) =          5  mod 5 = 0
    p(  9) =         30  mod 5 = 0
    p( 14) =        135  mod 5 = 0
    p( 19) =        490  mod 5 = 0
