  p(7k+5) ≡ 0 (mod H_forb_1):
    p(  5) =          7  mod 7 = 0
    p( 12) =         77  mod 7 = 0
    p( 19) =        490  mod 7 = 0
    p( 26) =       2436  mod 7 = 0
